.3</span> 标题：瞭望塔、塔楼、塔（watchtower, tower）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：אַלְמָן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：’alman)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">ISA 13:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בַּחַן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：bachan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:14\">ISA 32:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִגְדָּל, מִגְדֹּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：migdal, migdol)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:9\">JDG 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:17\">JDG 8:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:51\">JDG 9:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:51\">JDG 9:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:52\">JDG 9:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:52\">JDG 9:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:17\">2KI 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:9\">2KI 17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:8\">2KI 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr27:25\">1CH 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:6\">2CH 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:9\">2CH 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:15\">2CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:4\">2CH 27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:5\">2CH 32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:1\">NEH 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:1\">NEH 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:11\">NEH 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:25\">NEH 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:26\">NEH 3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:27\">NEH 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:38\">NEH 12:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:39\">NEH 12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:39\">NEH 12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:13\">PSA 48:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:4\">PSA 61:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:4\">SNG 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:13\">SNG 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:5\">SNG 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:5\">SNG 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:10\">SNG 8:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:15\">ISA 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:25\">ISA 30:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:18\">ISA 33:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:38\">JER 31:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:4\">EZK 26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:9\">EZK 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:11\">EZK 27:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:10\">ZEC 14:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מָצוֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：matsor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:1\">HAB 2:1</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִצְפֶּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mitspeh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:8\">ISA 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:24\">2CH 20:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：פִּנָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：pinah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:15\">2CH 26:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:16\">ZEP 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:6\">ZEP 3:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שֶׁמֶשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：shemesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:12\">ISA 54:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：πύργος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：purgos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:33\">MAT 21:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:1\">MRK 12:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:4\">LUK 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:28\">LUK 14:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob13:14\">TOB 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob13:17\">TOB 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt1:3\">JDT 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt1:14\">JDT 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt7:5\">JDT 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt7:32\">JDT 7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:33\">1MA 1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:60\">1MA 4:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:5\">1MA 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:5\">1MA 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:65\">1MA 5:65</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:33\">1MA 13:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:43\">1MA 13:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc16:10\">1MA 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:18\">2MA 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:20\">2MA 10:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:22\">2MA 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc10:36\">2MA 10:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc13:5\">2MA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Macc14:41\">2MA 14:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc2:27\">3MA 2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc13:6\">4MA 13:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd1:52\">1ES 1:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd4:4\">1ES 4:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：σκοπή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：skopē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir37:14\">SIR 37:14</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/PTZ-0069_watchtower_model.jpg\" alt=\"城墙上的守望塔模型\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">城墙上的守望塔模型 (© Ray Pritz by United Bible Societies)</figcaption></figure>瞭望塔是一座很高的建筑物，顶部有一个瞭望台。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>城墙每隔一段距离就建有一个瞭望塔，用来戒备靠近的敌人。城中的守军还可以从瞭望塔上对进攻者的侧面进行攻击。有时，私人产业也建有塔楼作为保护。另参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">2.19.3 射击台、攻城塔 (firing platform, siege tower)&lt;REALIA:2.19.3&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在许多语言中，“塔楼”一词仅仅是指“很高的建筑”（当然不是指摩天大楼）。在其他情况下，把它译为“很高的平台”或“很高的瞭望台”可能更合适。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">ISA 13:22</a> 中，希伯来文<em>’alman</em> 的字面意思是“他的寡妇”。这个词与意为“宫殿”的希伯来文词语非常相像（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.4 宫殿 (palace)&lt;REALIA:3.4&gt;</a> 中的<em>’armon</em> ）。我们不清楚是这里的文本出现了问题，还是作者有意互换了两个字母，以表示“荒凉”的意思（参瓦尔德［de Waard］，《〈以赛亚书手册〉》（<em>A Handbook on Isaiah</em> ），第61页）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:24\">2CH 20:24</a> ：虽然有些译本把希伯来文<em>mitspeh</em> 译为“塔楼”或“瞭望塔”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> ），但<em>mitspeh</em> 可能只是一个天然形成的、视野开阔的高点，因此可译为“旷野的瞭望塔”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）、“俯瞰旷野的地方”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> ）、“他们可以看到旷野的一个地方”（如 <abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 将这个词译为“一座小山，从山上面可以看到旷野”。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>pinah</em> 的字面意思是“角落”。在本词条的参考经文中，该词不一定指某个独立的构筑物，而仅仅是城墙的一个转角。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:16\">ZEP 1:16</a> 中，有些译本将这个词译为“角楼”（如<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ），还有译本的译法比较笼统，作“高耸的城垛”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 直译；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> 的译法类似）。</p>\n<p>有些较早的译本把<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:5\">ISA 21:5</a> 中的希伯来文<em>tsafith</em> 译为“瞭望塔”（“watchtower”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"King James Version (1611)\">KJV</abbr> ）。现在，学者普遍认为这个词的意思是“地毯”（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.17 地毯、毯子 (carpet, rug)&lt;REALIA:5.17&gt;</a> ）。</p>\n<p>在新约中，希腊文<em>purgos</em> 可以指任何类型的塔，包括用于军事目的或者供守望者保护收成的塔（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.1.11 瞭望楼 (watchtower)&lt;REALIA:1.1.11&gt;</a> ）。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:4\">LUK 13:4</a> 中的塔可能是耶路撒冷古城墙的一部分。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
